```
use core::matter::{tables::Codex, Matter}

// usage
Codex::Blake3_256.code();
```

The above becomes a problem once we introduce another Codex.

*After*

```
use core::matter::{tables as matter, Matter}

// usage
matter::Codex::Blake3_256.code();
```

We can use this namespacing method for our common substructures.

